  "description": "Outdoor Dual Band AP/CPE, Data Rate up to 1200Mbps, 802.11n/ac",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Description",
      "text": "N52Q is the outdoor dual-band / dual concurrent AP/CPE with built-in or external N type female connector. External antenna connector gives more options to meet different application. The unique software controlled PoE out helps to reduce the installation and maintain cost. N52Q is equipped with pre-installed the popular open source \"OpenWrt\" to give you freedom to modify for your needs."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Description",
      "text": "Thanks to the software controlled PoE out, you don't need an extra Ethernet cable to power another N52Q. You can use PoE out LAN port to provide 24VDC to power on. Make sure that connected device supports input passive PoE 24VDC before enable the pass through from the firmware."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Features",
      "text": "Dual-band 2.4 GHz + 5 GHz\nData transfer rate 1200 Mbps\nSoftware controlled PoE out\nExtra USB port\nOpenWrt firmware"
    }
  ],
